Re: 中高級寫作到底要怎麼通過啊
#5/6



Just can't stay away

註冊日期:2006/01/06 00:42
 所屬群組：
註冊會員  	
文章: 141
等級: 10; EXP: 92HP : 0 / 248MP : 47 / 8366



Another suggestion (something I learnt also in high school) - for your body paragraphs (中間三段), you can follow the "SEXI" structure (isn't it easy to remember? ;) )topic Sentence (stating what you're going to talk about in that particular paragraph IN ONE CLEAR SENTENCE)Explanation (explain your topic sentence further)eXamples (like cin said - give supporting evidence)Implications (for example, implications on the society, the novel, whatever...depending on the nature of your essay)But since I used this mainly for my 1000-word essays, your 英檢 word limit of 150-180 is really not a lot, maybe you just want to be concise and to the point, and avoid using unnecessary descriptive words like you're composing a piece of creative writing or something (unless that's what you're told to do).All the best! :)(ps apologies for the lack of Chinese - this keyboard is not capable of Chinese characters :p)


    	    	
	    2006/05/31 02:53






