個人資料



Re: 中高級寫作到底要怎麼通過啊
#6/6



Quite a regular

註冊日期:2006/06/21 04:14
 所屬群組：
註冊會員  	
文章: 43
等級: 5; EXP: 35HP : 0 / 108MP : 14 / 3528










What you need is probably a guide that will illustrate to you step-by-step those basic techniques involved in English composition. To meet the standards emphasized by GEPT (i.e., 遣詞，妥切及靈活運用句構，內容切題，全文組織完整，連貫通順), such a guide should cover topics dealing with diction, dexterous use of different sentence structures in presenting one’s views, and various methods of organizing information in a paragraph. An ideal guide in this nature should also provide you with sufficient exercises to practice all such techniques introduced. I noticed lately from a new-book announcement made by 博客來(http://www.books.com.tw/exep/prod/booksfile.php?item=0010334729#basic) that there is such a guide that meets the requirements mentioned above. Perhaps you may wish to borrow a copy of this book from a library nearby your school and do browse through its table of contents to see whether or not this is the book you are looking for. HTH.


    	    	
	    2006/06/22 03:28






